Cheerios, Gluten Free, Cereal with Whole Grain Oats, 12 oz Box

4.3 out of 5 stars 9 customer reviews
Ships from and sold by AmazonFresh.
  • CEREAL: Wholesome breakfast that's a good source of iron, calcium and fiber
  • GLUTEN FREE: Gluten free and simply made without artificial flavors or colors
  • WHOLE GRAIN: Made with 100% whole grain oats and fortified with 12 essential vitamins and minerals
  • HEART HEALTHY: Three grams of soluble fiber daily from whole grain oat foods, like Cheerios cereal, in a diet low in saturated fat and cholesterol, may reduce the risk of heart disease. Cheerios cereal provides 1 gram per serving
  • Perfect as first finger food or a gluten free snack

Important information

Ingredients

Whole Grain Oats, Corn Starch, Sugar, Salt, Tripotassium Phosphate. Vitamin E (mixed tocopherols) Added to Preserve Freshness. Vitamins and Minerals: Calcium Carbonate, Iron and Zinc (mineral nutrients), Vitamin C (sodium ascorbate), A B Vitamin (niacinamide), Vitamin B6 (pyridoxine hydrochloride), Vitamin A (palmitate), Vitamin B1 (thiamin mononitrate), A B Vitamin (folic acid), Vitamin B12, Vitamin D3.

5.0 out of 5 starsThese are cheerios, if you don't know what that means.... just get a box and try them.
September 29, 2017
Yup, these are cheerios. If you don't know what Cheerios are, just go ahead and buy a box. They are great is a baggie with raisins and nuts, superb in an oversized bowl with milk, and only marginally annoying when a toddler dumps them in the back seat of your car.

I prefer them with cut up strawberries for breakfast and am still trying to find the perfect heart shaped bowl to complete the experience.
